      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior paint and body are flawless with no scratches, dents, or chips. The interior is in pristine condition with no signs of wear on the upholstery, dashboard, or carpets. Mechanically, the car performs as new and has been meticulously maintained.",
